      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TAYLOR MADE BLUE (1) is an honest type rarely out of the money, scoring at this track (19.24) last time and making it two straight wins. Rates strongly and will go close from the inside draw. WRITTEN IN GOLD (2) had been in great form but was out of the placings last run, finishing fifth (22.89) in a NG at this track. Generally safe to begin but was always well back last time. Has a good record here at this journey. Worth following up. HOVERING (3) is worth forgiving for his last effort when fifth (30.54) at Richmond over 520m. Solid winning record at this trip. Shapes as one to consider. OVER REACTION (7) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three spot most recently.",
